c: 6
v: 19
t: "Ask ňĻthem, O Prophetňļ, ‚ÄúWho is the best witness?‚ÄĚ Say, ‚ÄúAllah is! He is a Witness between me and you. And this Quran has been revealed to me so that, with it, I may warn you and whoever it reaches. Do you ňĻpagansňļ testify that there are other gods besides Allah?‚ÄĚ ňĻThenňļ say, ‚ÄúI will never testify ňĻto thisňļ!‚ÄĚ ňĻAndňļ say, ‚ÄúThere is only One God. And I totally reject whatever ňĻidolsňļ you associate with Him.‚ÄĚ"